Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Plays an [effect](Effect_%28decl%29 "Effect (decl)") on a particular location of the entity.

Usage
-----

*void* playEffect( *string* **effectName** , *string* **boneName** , *float* **loop** )

Parameters
----------

-   [effectName] - Name of effect to play.
-   [boneName] - Skeleton location to play the effect at.
-   [loop] - Whether to loop the effect.

Examples
--------

    $my_entity.playEffect( "fire64", "joint01", 1 );

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values.

